{"tid":2505822,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"50歲前TVB綠葉跪地拜師 萬梓良豪爆送1萬蚊人仔","createTime":"2021-04-27T02:03:05.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-27T02:18:49.000Z","uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"0fec5d4351dda6c39ffa6f981477c0c1cca1632b","tid":2505822,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:03:05.000Z","msg":"內地電影《創業大贏家》日前進行開機儀式，電影由萬梓良、林子聰、林敬剛等人演出。儀式中出現插曲，林敬剛突然跪地向萬梓良拜師！<br />\n<br />\n萬梓良坐在椅子上，林敬剛恭敬地跪在地上，萬梓良更為徒弟改名「林奔」，他說：「奔向前，勇往直前。」奉茶時，萬梓良發揮搞笑本色：「係咪好熱啲水，都未正式奉茶，就想謀害我，快啲加啲水啦！」萬梓良飲茶前拍拍林敬剛的頭，再把少量的茶倒在徒弟頭上，氣派十足！萬梓良又豪言：「做咗咁耐咖哩啡，TVB唔捧你，我捧你！」最後他拿出一疊銀紙，共一萬元人民幣，送給林敬剛做見面禮！<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">63歲的萬梓良此前收過三個徒弟，分別是周星馳、林家棟及姜皓文</span>，三人現在都達到不同的成就。而林敬剛現年50歲，在無綫工作逾廿年，多數是做綠葉角色，他在劇中常飾演惡霸或奸角，因而有「御用惡人」之稱。"},{"pid":"7b0afa97804c1a0d0886634b527717d411cd58a3","tid":2505822,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:05:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/9yzD6RHH1YHW8Jj72bXhzQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-04/d41ca390-a660-11eb-bf4f-d45453fb6f77\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2F9yzD6RHH1YHW8Jj72bXhzQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-04%2Fd41ca390-a660-11eb-bf4f-d45453fb6f77&h=51c420d2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n50歲先嚟拜師？<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/rfh2hn4IG1cVrCDeoKXzbg--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-04/f12e32a0-a660-11eb-afbf-9c16861a866e\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Frfh2hn4IG1cVrCDeoKXzbg--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-04%2Ff12e32a0-a660-11eb-afbf-9c16861a866e&h=ace3c505&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n摸摸徒弟個頭。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/U0KlMEk_N7RivraJz_pzyQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-04/f12ecee0-a660-11eb-aeff-710d4db12d05\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FU0KlMEk_N7RivraJz_pzyQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-04%2Ff12ecee0-a660-11eb-aeff-710d4db12d05&h=3d53c759&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n再送1萬蚊人仔！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/WHAHykk.ioAbrkSPuzSbBQ--/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw/https://s.yimg.com/os/creatr-uploaded-images/2021-04/098742b0-a661-11eb-bb1f-f07d44d5e3b0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2FWHAHykk.ioAbrkSPuzSbBQ--%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjt3PTk2MDtjZj13ZWJw%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fos%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2021-04%2F098742b0-a661-11eb-bb1f-f07d44d5e3b0&h=f25a4d85&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n林敬剛多做綠葉角色，有「御用惡人」之稱。<br />\n<br />\n點解D相可以濛到咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"06810877b33f5f964c5297c20f439ccb14835222","tid":2505822,"uid":153781,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:05:46.000Z","msg":"乖 仔～～"},{"pid":"e6dc8deedfb23cd2f96be5496cbea3b85e043191","tid":2505822,"uid":133529,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:06:10.000Z","msg":"你做乜撚野唔食飯呀"},{"pid":"99e5b502cc7219d51eb5eef675c7161b476444e1","tid":2505822,"uid":16957,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-27T02:07:45.000Z","msg":"我屌呀 嗰個係萬梓良 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />？"},{"pid":"198cd276470e8a8ff2ffd6ada4c3103ecab10fcb","tid":2505822,"uid":71166,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"cit